    "assertion": "At 1 kb autosomal resolution, SINE fraction positively correlates with median GTEx expression after GC residualization (partial Spearman rho ~ +0.18, p << 0.001). The SINE fraction carries a GC-independent positive expression signal — consistent with Alu exonization and enhancer co-option literature.",
